WEBVTT

00:00:27.716 --> 00:00:30.759
akhtstn yuli nayntsn hundert zibn un nayntsik,

00:00:30.770 --> 00:00:33.307
intervyu mit MONSIEUR Hershko-

00:00:33.307 --> 00:00:35.425
Herman Hershkovitsh,

00:00:35.462 --> 00:00:37.380
ikh heys EVI Frukhter,

00:00:37.605 --> 00:00:42.426
undz, mir zenen do in Antverpn, in Belgye, un dos intervyu vet zikh opshpiln in yidish.

00:00:46.093 --> 00:00:50.140
mayn nomen iz EVI Frukhter, undz ze'mir haynt dem akhtsntn yuli,

00:00:50.140 --> 00:00:52.038
nayntsn hundert zibn un nayntsik.

00:00:52.038 --> 00:00:55.363
ikh fir do a intervyu mit MONSIEUR Herman Hershkovitsh,

00:00:55.363 --> 00:00:56.989
in Antverpn, Belgye.

00:01:02.293 --> 00:01:04.970
ir kent nokh a mol iberzogn ayer nomen bite?

00:01:05.330 --> 00:01:07.197
Herman Hershkovitsh.

00:01:07.271 --> 00:01:10.320
un vi azoy shraybt men Hershkovitsh?

00:01:08.975 --> 00:01:10.319
vi azoy me vil.

00:01:11.793 --> 00:01:13.728
un ir zent geboyrn ven?

00:01:13.937 --> 00:01:15.520
akht un tsvontsik

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:18.335
hu- yuni akht un tsvontsik.

00:01:18.847 --> 00:01:20.731
un vi zent ir haynt, vi alt?

00:01:22.020 --> 00:01:23.871
nayn un zekhtsik yor.

00:01:24.483 --> 00:01:26.623
un in velkhe shtot zent ir geboyrn?

00:01:26.508 --> 00:01:27.616
Orsheve.

00:01:27.622 --> 00:01:30.789
vi azoy shraybt men dos?

00:01:28.837 --> 00:01:30.924
oyf tshekhish, IRSHAVA.

00:01:31.470 --> 00:01:33.321
un in velkhn land?

00:01:33.562 --> 00:01:38.231
damolts iz es gevezn in Tshekhoslovakay, un haynt iz es Ukraine.

00:01:38.557 --> 00:01:41.268
tsvishn iz es gevezn oykhet, in krig,

00:01:41.477 --> 00:01:45.420
bazets fun di ukrainer un dan shpeter fun di ungarn.

00:01:46.843 --> 00:01:51.984
koydem kol MONSIEUR Hershkovitsh, efsher kent ir undz a bisl dertseyln fun ayer heym?

00:01:52.091 --> 00:01:56.642
vi ir hot gevoynt, vi azoy ir hot gelebt far di krig, far nayntsn hundert akht un draysik.

00:01:57.997 --> 00:02:04.117
a normal Tshekh- lebn, azoy vi in Tshekhoslovakay hot zikh gefirt, zeyer a demokratishes lebn.

00:02:05.439 --> 00:02:10.665
un azoy tsi zogn, keyne problemen.

00:02:11.447 --> 00:02:12.051
⟨ikh meyn kh-⟩

00:02:12.051 --> 00:02:17.856
problemen meyn ikh yidish problemen, vayl problemen hot yeder mentsh farshidens,

00:02:17.893 --> 00:02:20.520
ober ikh meyn vegn yidishe problemen.

00:02:21.167 --> 00:02:22.866
un dos iz gegangen

00:02:23.073 --> 00:02:25.194
biz di krig hot BEGINEN.

00:02:25.925 --> 00:02:27.573
dan hobn undz,

00:02:27.782 --> 00:02:31.894
in nayn un draysik hobn men di tshekhn aroysgevorfn,

00:02:33.333 --> 00:02:36.399
zenen gekumen di ukrainer,

00:02:37.738 --> 00:02:40.415
ukrainer fun Kiev, ukrainer.

00:02:40.843 --> 00:02:46.187
vayl dos folk vos se lebt iz a rutenisher, di di rutener lebn dort.

00:02:46.901 --> 00:02:52.700
und di tshekhn hot men aroysgevorfn,

00:02:53.263 --> 00:02:57.324
nisht me hot zey geheysn aroysgeyn, nor me hot zey faktish aroysgevorfn,

00:03:00.688 --> 00:03:05.849
un se hot zikh BEGINEN mit zeyer bazetsung,

00:03:05.849 --> 00:03:09.781
zey hobn gekrign a AUTONOMIE, di ukrainer hobn gekrign

00:03:09.781 --> 00:03:12.090
fun HItler an AUTONOMIE in MUNCHEN.

00:03:13.192 --> 00:03:18.924
zey hobn afile nisht gekent nokhzogn dos vort AUTONOMIE, hobn zey gezogt, "mir hobn gekrign a oytomobil."

00:03:20.617 --> 00:03:22.310
und

00:03:22.355 --> 00:03:24.206
azoy hobn zey BEGINEN

00:03:24.617 --> 00:03:27.261
shoyn diskriminatsye tsu yidn.

00:03:28.447 --> 00:03:36.255
di yinglekh azoy vi ikh, me- yinglekh, di di di vos zenen gegangen in tshekhishe shule, vayl se bay undz gevezn a rutenishe shule oykhet,

00:03:36.648 --> 00:03:38.347
dos heyst a,

00:03:38.555 --> 00:03:40.231
a shule vu me hot gelernt

00:03:40.231 --> 00:03:42.448
rusish, ⟨tsiri⟩ alfabet.

00:03:42.690 --> 00:03:44.400
nisht azoy vi di tshekhishe,

00:03:44.400 --> 00:03:45.941
der lataynishe alfabet.

00:03:46.487 --> 00:03:48.607
und

00:03:51.313 --> 00:03:53.872
az me hot gemuzt shoyn kenen

00:03:54.941 --> 00:03:57.720
dem tsiri alfabet, shraybn, lezn,

00:03:59.177 --> 00:04:05.920
nisht me vet enk lernen, ets vet kenen, ets vet, se vet araynkumen in dem. neyn, undz ho'mir shoyn gemuzt kenen,

00:04:06.298 --> 00:04:09.009
un me hot in di shule ZOGAR

00:04:09.234 --> 00:04:12.081
ofitsyel ⟨geyidlt⟩.

00:04:13.875 --> 00:04:18.561
di lererin hot undz ⟨geyidlt⟩. tsum bayshpil se geven a fal dort,

00:04:19.157 --> 00:04:21.733
di shule, dos hoyz fun di shule,

00:04:21.975 --> 00:04:25.918
iz mayne gotzelike eltern's hoyz gevezn.

00:04:28.151 --> 00:04:29.647
un

00:04:29.855 --> 00:04:34.102
dort zenen geve- gegangen farshidene klasn, groyse un kleyne.

00:04:35.627 --> 00:04:44.143
iz gevezn dort a a yunger, nisht keyn, nisht keyn yidish yunge, a a kristlekher yunger,

00:04:45.195 --> 00:04:47.721
vos er iz gevezn dos drite

00:04:47.793 --> 00:04:49.576
i- mol shoyn

00:04:50.088 --> 00:04:53.778
in di in di zelbe klas, dos heyst dray yor elter fun undz.

00:04:54.020 --> 00:04:56.562
un er iz gevezn a fester geboy,

00:04:57.564 --> 00:04:59.415
und

00:04:59.876 --> 00:05:04.764
er hot ongehoybn tsu tshepen zikh mit di kleyne kinder, raysn di peyes, un azoy vayter.

00:05:05.529 --> 00:05:13.083
un ikh hob zeyer gut gekent ZOGAR zayn foter, flegt tsu undz arayntsukumen in der heym vegn arbet un vegn nokh andere zakh,

00:05:13.781 --> 00:05:15.530
hob ikh tsun im gezogt,

00:05:15.705 --> 00:05:20.812
"VARUM zolstu, VARUM tustu dos? biz haynt ho'mir, ho'mir undz gut geven, vos iz yetst dos?"

00:05:21.105 --> 00:05:23.985
hot er mir gegebn a shpay in ponem.

00:05:24.564 --> 00:05:26.955
azoy vi ikh bin gevezn genug ⟨flink⟩,

00:05:27.770 --> 00:05:32.721
un ikh, ikh hob in mir gehat nokh dem

00:05:32.721 --> 00:05:34.903
kharakter nisht tsu lozn zikh,

00:05:35.229 --> 00:05:37.007
ikh gegebn a kop

00:05:37.035 --> 00:05:38.683
in beyn-fus.

00:05:39.347 --> 00:05:43.189
un er hot zikh gegebn a, a khalesh avek, vayl,

00:05:45.388 --> 00:05:48.082
hot di lererin undz nisht bashtroft.

00:05:49.269 --> 00:05:51.035
nor zi hot gezogt,

00:05:51.243 --> 00:05:56.199
"shemt ets enk nisht, ets lozt enk fun di yidn? vos far a mentshn zent ets?"

00:05:56.407 --> 00:05:57.583
un azoy vayter.

00:05:57.639 --> 00:05:59.805
un me hot farshidene,

00:05:59.805 --> 00:06:04.147
tsum bayshpil bashnaydn zikh, hot me- hot hot men in di shule

00:06:04.794 --> 00:06:06.628
geMENTIONt.

00:06:06.903 --> 00:06:09.288
me hot er nisht gelernt als oyfgabe,

00:06:09.288 --> 00:06:13.203
ober zi hot dos gezogt.

00:06:13.203 --> 00:06:14.255
un azoy vayter.

00:06:17.147 --> 00:06:19.993
nakher hobn di ungarn,

00:06:21.517 --> 00:06:25.933
nokh farshidene monatn vos zey hobn dort gehersht, di

00:06:26.411 --> 00:06:31.859
SITSHOVIKES hobn geheysn zeyere militer., oder vi azoy,

00:06:31.862 --> 00:06:33.139
di ukrainisher.

00:06:35.355 --> 00:06:37.560
hot Ungarn zey aroysgevorfn,

00:06:37.667 --> 00:06:40.598
un zi hot bazetst Karpatn-Rusland

00:06:41.008 --> 00:06:44.968
biz me hot undz deportirt.

00:06:45.480 --> 00:06:47.769
un ven me hot undz deportirt

00:06:48.062 --> 00:06:50.419
zenen nokh gevezn di ungarn.

00:06:50.795 --> 00:06:58.822
ir hot gefilt a groysn diferents ven di ungarn zenen arayngekumen nokh di ukrainer? se iz geven der antisemitizm shtarker oder?

00:06:57.579 --> 00:07:00.527
der ibergang iz gevezn

00:07:01.562 --> 00:07:02.839
a laykhte,

00:07:04.143 --> 00:07:07.850
trots dem vos dort bay undz zenen gevezn yidn

00:07:08.227 --> 00:07:13.233
vos zey gedenken nokh dem estraykh-ungarishn, dos heyst der der

00:07:13.644 --> 00:07:15.630
di farn-krigedikn

00:07:15.872 --> 00:07:20.423
Estraykh, vayl dort iz oykh gevezn a mol Estraykh-Ungarn nokh far di tshekhn,

00:07:23.448 --> 00:07:27.020
un se gevezn zeyer gut demolts far yidn.

00:07:27.347 --> 00:07:34.229
zen- men, ven di ungarn zenen arayngekumen, iz men akegn gegangen, di yidn, mit broyt un mit

00:07:34.229 --> 00:07:37.297
zalts un UNK.

00:07:37.809 --> 00:07:40.481
zenen di, arayngekumen di

00:07:40.481 --> 00:07:44.098
KOKOSH CHENDERERS, dos zenen GENDARMERIE,

00:07:44.154 --> 00:07:47.197
vos zey trogn hutn un oyf dem hobn zey fun a hon

00:07:47.242 --> 00:07:49.475
federn, ruft men zey KOKOSH,

00:07:49.475 --> 00:07:51.641
oyf ungarish heyst a hon KOKOSH.

00:07:53.604 --> 00:07:56.940
un zey hobn oysgeflikt un oysgerisn di yidn di berd.

00:07:57.705 --> 00:08:00.011
hot men zey gefregt baym davenen, "nu!

00:08:00.287 --> 00:08:06.587
reb Moyshe ir hot azoy fil gehaltn fun di ungarn, ir hot azoy sheyn geredt, nu zet ir vi vi ir zet oys?"

00:08:06.587 --> 00:08:08.567
zogt er, "se nisht di zelbe."

00:08:11.643 --> 00:08:17.300
un vi azoy iz es vayter gegangen in di shule? di shule iz gevorn ungarish? me hot gemuzt lernen in ungarish?

00:08:16.605 --> 00:08:19.670
in di shule hot men gelernt ungarish.

00:08:20.672 --> 00:08:23.130
dos heyst ir hot vider gemuzt ibershteln fun,

00:08:22.308 --> 00:08:27.416
iberge- yo. fun ukrainish vider ariber in ungarish un azoy ho'mir geendikt di shule.

00:08:28.282 --> 00:08:34.689
ober in di shule iz nisht geven keyn problem, iber hoypt yidn nisht, dos hot der, der der problem hot nisht gelebt.

00:08:35.471 --> 00:08:39.426
biz dan es hot ayngefangen in algemeyn der

00:08:39.426 --> 00:08:43.768
MUNKHENER gezetsn gegn iber di yidn.

00:08:44.634 --> 00:08:45.523
koydem

00:08:46.085 --> 00:08:47.514
hot men ale

00:08:47.857 --> 00:08:49.893
shatlekhe gesheftn

00:08:50.118 --> 00:08:54.433
un ayngeshtelter, baamter

00:08:54.489 --> 00:08:58.196
vos zenen gevezn in di shtat, aheymgeshikt.

00:08:58.809 --> 00:09:00.626
dan hot men gesheftn

00:09:01.121 --> 00:09:05.250
vos hot gehert tsu der shtat, tsum bayshpil der alkohol

00:09:06.183 --> 00:09:08.405
iz geven a shtatlikhe zakh,

00:09:08.883 --> 00:09:10.548
hot men tsugenumen,

00:09:10.655 --> 00:09:13.940
un dan hot men tsugenumen gesheftn,

00:09:14.098 --> 00:09:15.830
un dan hot men oykhet,

00:09:16.140 --> 00:09:19.087
azoy iz es ⟨suksesiv⟩ gegangen foroys,

00:09:19.413 --> 00:09:23.221
un me hot tsugenumen di verkshtatn

00:09:24.982 --> 00:09:25.857
UNK

00:09:25.033 --> 00:09:27.290
vos hot ayer foter getun?

00:09:25.893 --> 00:09:27.258
undz ho'mir gehat

00:09:27.258 --> 00:09:28.926
a mebl fabrik,

00:09:29.235 --> 00:09:30.529
a tishleray,

00:09:32.424 --> 00:09:34.038
me hot es geshlosn.

00:09:35.580 --> 00:09:37.043
ho'mir genumen

00:09:37.470 --> 00:09:38.899
a ⟨shtroy-man⟩

00:09:40.271 --> 00:09:43.049
a ungar fun Ungarn,

00:09:44.338 --> 00:09:46.133
un er hot,

00:09:46.133 --> 00:09:49.378
dos hot geheysn a UNK oyf ungarish,

00:09:49.856 --> 00:09:54.795
un oyf zayn nomen ho'mir undz gearbet. er hot gekrign far dem a gehalt un azoy vayter.

00:09:55.475 --> 00:09:58.979
oykh der shokhn undzer vos zi hot gehat a holts-lager,

00:09:59.863 --> 00:10:02.001
hot gehat dem zelbn UNK.

00:10:03.052 --> 00:10:05.274
un azoy nokh hot men gearbet.

00:10:06.427 --> 00:10:08.092
un se dertsey-

00:10:07.119 --> 00:10:10.516
der shtroyman iz geven a onshtendike mentshn, tsi er, oder

00:10:10.516 --> 00:10:13.883
ir hot oykh mit im tsutun gehat oykh mit im ANTISEMITISMUS?

00:10:11.270 --> 00:10:14.997
biz biz se hot

00:10:14.997 --> 00:10:17.002
angefangen

00:10:17.531 --> 00:10:20.006
az undz ze'mir shoyn gornisht.

00:10:21.328 --> 00:10:24.697
vayl me hot ongefangen shoyn frier, me hot angefangen

00:10:25.327 --> 00:10:28.983
tsu deportirn nokh Poyln, familyes,

00:10:29.630 --> 00:10:30.873
mit kinder,

00:10:30.980 --> 00:10:34.319
ZOGAR afile mener vos zenen gevezn in

00:10:34.319 --> 00:10:37.590
MONKOSAZE, dos heyst in arbayts-lager,

00:10:38.473 --> 00:10:41.454
unter militer, zey hobn gearbet far militer,

00:10:42.506 --> 00:10:44.284
hot men deportirt,

00:10:44.295 --> 00:10:46.382
NACH Poyln, fartribn, yo?

00:10:46.809 --> 00:10:49.790
hot ir perzenlekh oykh gemuzt epes tun far militer?

00:10:50.623 --> 00:10:56.034
ikh perzenlekh hob getun vayl se iz gevezn a,

00:10:56.293 --> 00:10:58.312
fun tsvelef yor on

00:10:58.503 --> 00:10:59.999
hot men gedarft geyn

00:11:00.258 --> 00:11:03.156
in a sort LEVENTE.

00:11:04.022 --> 00:11:09.771
der LEVENTE dos iz gevezn der nomen, ober in in undzer leb-tsayt

00:11:09.843 --> 00:11:12.498
nisht yidn hobn gehat gever,

00:11:12.510 --> 00:11:14.617
me hot zey gelernt militerishe zakhn,

00:11:14.653 --> 00:11:20.047
un undz hot men geheysn arbetn vos, vos se nor gevezn. eyn mol in der vokh ze'mir gegangen dort.

00:11:21.605 --> 00:11:23.645
vos badayt dos vort LEVENTE?

00:11:23.597 --> 00:11:26.392
dos iz oyf,

00:11:28.473 --> 00:11:30.982
dos iz di Hitler Yugnt oyf doytsh.

00:11:31.680 --> 00:11:35.201
ober yidn hot men genumen fun dem AGE,

00:11:35.645 --> 00:11:37.310
un me hot mit zey gearbet.

00:11:38.430 --> 00:11:41.023
dos heyst s'iz oykh geven a sort arbayts-dinst.

00:11:40.607 --> 00:11:44.702
yo, dos iz der arbayts-dinst, yo. dos vos me hot genumen

00:11:46.158 --> 00:11:49.759
arbayts-lager, bay di ungarn,

00:11:49.759 --> 00:11:54.252
di mentshn vos zenen militer FLIKHT, yidn.

00:11:54.377 --> 00:11:56.903
un di vos zenen militer-FLIKHT,

00:11:57.347 --> 00:11:59.496
nisht yidn, hot men gelernt

00:11:59.496 --> 00:12:02.913
militerish umgeyn,

00:12:02.913 --> 00:12:04.530
mit gever un azoy vayter.

00:12:09.260 --> 00:12:15.161
in ayer dorf zenen geven hoyptzekhlekh khsidishe yidn, oder farshidene sortn yidn?

00:12:14.002 --> 00:12:15.363
farshidene.

00:12:16.567 --> 00:12:20.190
bay undz iz gevezn tsvey khsidishe

00:12:21.258 --> 00:12:24.205
tipn yidn, se gevezn satmare yidn,

00:12:25.190 --> 00:12:27.783
un se iz gevezn Spinker yidn.

00:12:27.873 --> 00:12:32.964
yedere hot gelebt sholem eyns mitn andern. keyn krigeray vi es

00:12:33.037 --> 00:12:37.605
pasirt in andere shtet, ZOGAR in Amerike,

00:12:38.083 --> 00:12:41.604
meynstns dort, iz bay undz nisht gevezn.

00:12:43.668 --> 00:12:46.092
un ir hot gehat a rebe oykhet dort?

00:12:47.617 --> 00:12:50.480
azoy vi yeder eyner hot gehat, yo.

00:12:52.072 --> 00:12:57.787
nor in krigs tsayt bin ikh nisht gegangen in di yeshive.

00:12:59.210 --> 00:13:03.541
vayl ikh bin gevezn der eltster fun di yinglekh,

00:13:03.935 --> 00:13:07.659
vayl a bruder un a shvester zenen geforn nokh Belgyen.

00:13:08.272 --> 00:13:10.477
in velkhn yor?

00:13:09.133 --> 00:13:10.596
akht un draysik.

00:13:11.613 --> 00:13:13.210
far vos zenen zey avekgeforn?

00:13:14.280 --> 00:13:19.826
di shvester iz geforn aher vayl undz ho'mir do gehat a onkl un a tante, vegn a shidekh.

00:13:19.983 --> 00:13:21.682
iz zi shoyn geblibn do,

00:13:22.025 --> 00:13:24.669
un der bruder iz geforn shpeter

00:13:25.164 --> 00:13:29.833
ven se hot, me hot geshmuest az se vet zayn a mobilezirung,

00:13:30.648 --> 00:13:31.790
far krig.

00:13:32.893 --> 00:13:36.718
iz er gekumen nokh Belgyen un

00:13:37.466 --> 00:13:41.224
mayn gotzelike muter, er iz geven dos eltste kind

00:13:42.427 --> 00:13:43.468
in UNK.

00:13:43.558 --> 00:13:47.265
un di di gants Orsheve

00:13:47.439 --> 00:13:49.678
f- froyen, yidishe froyen, farshtendlekh,

00:13:49.970 --> 00:13:54.791
hot zeyer imer gerimt dayn, tsu mayn gotzeliker muter,

00:13:54.898 --> 00:13:58.757
hobn zey gezogt, "yo, dayn Avrom Simkhele, azolekhs iz nisht do."

00:14:01.327 --> 00:14:03.667
un ven der ban hot gefifn,

00:14:04.618 --> 00:14:08.392
hot imer mayn gotzelike muter geveynt.

00:14:08.583 --> 00:14:16.425
az di ban hot ir avekgefirt ir kind. yo.

00:14:16.262 --> 00:14:19.294
velkhe shvester iz mitgeforn? vi azoy hot zi geheysn?

00:14:19.282 --> 00:14:23.800
Tsirl. Tsila. yo.

00:14:25.003 --> 00:14:27.512
zi iz fun do deportirt gevorn

00:14:29.340 --> 00:14:33.164
nokh Oyshvits, Birkenoy,

00:14:34.098 --> 00:14:40.134
un der bruder iz geven bahaltn a shtikl tsayt in Frankraykh,

00:14:40.275 --> 00:14:44.741
biz tsu der italyenisher kapitelatsye, un dan iz er gekumen

00:14:44.983 --> 00:14:49.736
NACH Oyshvits, DEN WIR hobn bakumen fun im a ⟨druk-sort⟩

00:14:51.952 --> 00:14:53.988
durkh dem Yidishn

00:14:57.116 --> 00:15:02.578
Komitet, oder vi azoy hot es geheysn dort, durkh dem Yid- Yudi- Yudishn-Rat

00:15:02.820 --> 00:15:05.649
Berlin, az,

00:15:06.279 --> 00:15:12.230
vu er iz ongekumen ho'mir nisht gevust, nor d- shpeter ven undz ze'mir ongekumen ho'mir gevust vu dos iz.

00:15:12.540 --> 00:15:14.087
vayl undz ho'mir gekrign

00:15:14.210 --> 00:15:16.955
a a zelb-kartl tsu shraybn,

00:15:17.180 --> 00:15:20.769
un dos iz es gevezn, me iz ongekumen nokh

00:15:21.517 --> 00:15:23.385
nokh Oyshvits, Birkenoy,

00:15:26.411 --> 00:15:28.391
nor er iz nisht tsurikgekumen.

00:15:28.436 --> 00:15:30.860
mer ho'mir undz fun im nisht gehert.

00:15:33.498 --> 00:15:34.809
un di shvester

00:15:36.131 --> 00:15:38.538
iz dort gevezn, in Oyshvits,

00:15:38.730 --> 00:15:41.644
un zi hot geboyt Oyshvits,

00:15:41.885 --> 00:15:46.047
ven zi iz ahingekumen, vayl Oyshvits aleyn iz geven a militerishe KAZERNE,

00:15:46.205 --> 00:15:52.696
un dan hot men tsugeboyt oyf fertsik meter, fertsik kilometer kvadrat,

00:15:53.445 --> 00:15:55.127
tsu Birkenoy,

00:15:55.335 --> 00:16:01.100
un dort iz geven der fabrik vu me hot

00:16:01.460 --> 00:16:06.112
nisht fabritsirt, nor vu me hot geharget yidn.

00:16:08.295 --> 00:16:11.107
der farnikhtungs-fabrik iz dort gevezn.

00:16:12.227 --> 00:16:18.161
un zi hot geboyt di shtrasn dort, nokh mit andere. un me hot zey zeyer

00:16:19.213 --> 00:16:21.502
shlekht bahadnlt, tsum bayshpil,

00:16:26.452 --> 00:16:34.682
me hot genumen di shteyner mit vos me makht di shtrase, di kleyne sh- ikh veys nisht vi dos heyst in andere SHTRA- shprakhn,

00:16:35.025 --> 00:16:36.893
nor dos heyst SHOTER,

00:16:37.573 --> 00:16:40.284
di shteyner, dos zenen shoyn tseklapte shteyner,

00:16:40.998 --> 00:16:46.662
un zey hobn gevorfn, zey hobn getsilt in di kep fun di froyen,

00:16:48.828 --> 00:16:51.914
oder zey hobn genumen a tikhl,

00:16:51.917 --> 00:16:54.763
oder a UNK un zey hobn arayngeleygt a shteyn,

00:16:54.836 --> 00:16:59.100
un zey hobn gevorfn dem shteyn mit dem tsuzamen, un zey hobn gezogt,

00:16:59.325 --> 00:17:01.901
"loyf un khap es!"

00:17:02.649 --> 00:17:07.233
in tsvishn hobn zey ge- avekgeshosn, zey hobn zikh gelernt azoy shisn.

00:17:10.225 --> 00:17:17.290
un m- mayn shvester hot gekrign a infektsye oyfn fis. un demolts iz gevezn dort a shpitol

00:17:18.798 --> 00:17:23.517
nokh nisht keyn shpito- shpitol fun operat, ober forleyfike shpitol.

00:17:24.840 --> 00:17:33.136
un zi hot oykhet bald BEGINEN dort, se nisht geven azoy shreklekh oyf tsu lign,

00:17:33.210 --> 00:17:36.478
hot zi di mentshn dort geholfn.

00:17:37.344 --> 00:17:39.746
un azoy iz zi geblibn in dem shpitol,

00:17:39.746 --> 00:17:42.249
tsvishn hot men oyfgeboyt dem Birkenoy,

00:17:47.402 --> 00:17:49.972
un me hot gebrengt oykhet,

00:17:50.017 --> 00:17:53.285
in di tsayt hot men gebrengt

00:17:53.460 --> 00:17:58.365
vos me hot gekhapt yugoslavishe partizaners, froyen,

00:17:58.607 --> 00:18:02.499
iz geven a partizanke di BEGIN ven d- ven me hot zey gebrengt,

00:18:03.163 --> 00:18:05.773
un zey zenen zeyer mutike mentshn,

00:18:07.027 --> 00:18:08.422
a yunge

00:18:08.681 --> 00:18:10.481
sheyne, shtarke froy,

00:18:10.773 --> 00:18:14.447
hot men ir gegebn, tatuirt dem numer,

00:18:14.520 --> 00:18:19.358
hot zi nisht gelozt un zi hot gegebn a patsh dem yenikn.

00:18:19.768 --> 00:18:22.277
hot men zi tserisn oyf shtiker.

00:18:24.257 --> 00:18:25.908
VARUM zog ikh dos?

00:18:25.944 --> 00:18:27.367
vayl shpeter

00:18:27.367 --> 00:18:31.456
iz, hot men andere gebrengt un azoy vi mayn shvester hot gekent

00:18:31.682 --> 00:18:35.760
rutenish, tshekhish, slavish, in algemeyn,

00:18:36.525 --> 00:18:39.861
hot zi gezogt far di yugoslavishe meydlekh, " herts tsu.

00:18:41.132 --> 00:18:42.791
dos un dos hot pasirt,

00:18:42.791 --> 00:18:46.188
un vilst epes tun,

00:18:46.717 --> 00:18:48.956
lomir vartn di gelegnheyt."

00:18:50.295 --> 00:18:54.204
un azoy nokh hot zi oykh kenen gelernt yugoslavishe doktorin,

00:18:54.598 --> 00:18:57.726
UNK shpeter a rusishe doktorin, oder vi azoy,

00:18:57.726 --> 00:18:59.992
a tshekhishe doktorin iz oykh gevezn,

00:19:00.133 --> 00:19:01.174
zey hobn zikh gekent.

00:19:01.280 --> 00:19:06.253
ven me hot oyf- -gelezt dem shpitol vu zi iz gevezn,

00:19:08.317 --> 00:19:10.424
iz zi gevezn in a vashe-ROOM,

00:19:10.424 --> 00:19:15.635
un zi hot zikh dort getrofn mit tshekhishe doktorin.

00:19:17.058 --> 00:19:18.487
hot zi gezogt,

00:19:18.729 --> 00:19:20.968
"du kum tsu undz arayn."

00:19:22.813 --> 00:19:24.883
ikh gloyb nisht tsi me hot gevust,

00:19:25.260 --> 00:19:28.174
dos heyst tsu dem nisht yidishn shpitol.

00:19:28.770 --> 00:19:32.733
ikh gloyb nisht tsu zey hobn genoy gevust tsi zi iz a yidishe,

00:19:32.769 --> 00:19:34.302
vayl zi hot geheysn

00:19:34.305 --> 00:19:39.395
Hershkovitsh OVA SISIR, un dos iz a slavisher nomen,

00:19:40.110 --> 00:19:42.517
di yugoslavn heysn oykhet azoy.

00:19:42.590 --> 00:19:43.985
ober yedn fals,

00:19:44.058 --> 00:19:45.600
ikh gey nisht in dem arayn.

00:19:45.628 --> 00:19:49.639
zi iz dort gevezn in dem shpitol un zi iz geven farantvortlekh

00:19:50.353 --> 00:19:54.381
far der tsar fun di mentshn velkhe zenen in shpitol.

00:19:56.985 --> 00:20:01.401
iz yedn tog ven me hot gemakht apel,

00:20:02.638 --> 00:20:04.809
iz zi geven di farantvortlekhe,

00:20:04.967 --> 00:20:08.741
hot men ir gezogt, zolst visn, iz es yudn-reyn?

00:20:08.932 --> 00:20:10.934
az nisht iz dort do der koymen.

00:20:11.261 --> 00:20:16.723
zi iz nisht azoy geven dershrokn derfar, ober zi iz geven mutik un zi hot imer gezogt, yo.

00:20:18.180 --> 00:20:23.017
oykh in di ze- di zelbe tsayt iz gevezn di UNK

00:20:23.259 --> 00:20:26.746
vos me hot zi shpeter gevo- gezolt hengen

00:20:27.107 --> 00:20:29.346
un me hot zi farbrent,

00:20:30.735 --> 00:20:33.159
me hot zi gezolt farbrenen lebedik,

00:20:33.924 --> 00:20:35.415
ober tsvishn

00:20:35.460 --> 00:20:37.803
firn zi tsum farbrenen

00:20:37.805 --> 00:20:40.415
iz gefaln a koyl, me veyst nisht ver.

00:20:41.501 --> 00:20:47.438
zi hot mit mayn shvester kolaborirt.

00:20:47.438 --> 00:20:51.775
zi hot gearbet in dem politishn byuro.

00:20:51.778 --> 00:20:53.342
azoy hot es geheysn dort.

00:20:53.820 --> 00:20:56.227
zi hot gevust ven es geyt a

00:20:56.722 --> 00:20:58.066
a selektsye.

00:21:00.283 --> 00:21:02.195
hot zi gebrengt far

00:21:02.195 --> 00:21:08.023
a ruzh vos vos me hot gebrengt, vos me hot tsamgenumen fun di mentshn vos me hot zey farnikhtet,

00:21:08.332 --> 00:21:12.056
iz dort geven farshidene zakhn, ruzh un azoy vayter. hot zi gebrengt

00:21:12.180 --> 00:21:13.558
far di meydlekh,

00:21:13.665 --> 00:21:15.535
zoln zikh a bisl farbn,

00:21:15.535 --> 00:21:19.076
un afile royt papir farbik

00:21:19.537 --> 00:21:26.512
un vos meglekh hot zi farshtupt tsu mayn shvester in shpitol arayn

00:21:26.523 --> 00:21:27.496
tsvishn zey.

00:21:27.671 --> 00:21:33.487
un mayn shvester hobn di nisht yidishe heftlingen, vos zenen krank gevezn,

00:21:33.982 --> 00:21:38.685
zeyer respektirt, vayl zi iz geven zeyer gut tsu zey. zi iz geven a mame tsu zey.

00:21:38.876 --> 00:21:40.912
un a mamen farrat men nisht.

00:21:41.677 --> 00:21:43.241
un azoy iz dos gegangen.

00:21:44.833 --> 00:21:46.498
efsher STOPPED men a bisl?

00:21:47.043 --> 00:21:49.805
ayer shvester iz geven biz ven in Oyshvits?

00:21:51.617 --> 00:21:55.948
biz nisht, nisht biz tsu der bafrayung, vayl

00:21:56.443 --> 00:21:57.838
vayl me hot zey,

00:21:59.193 --> 00:22:04.064
detsember oder ven hot men zey evakuirt nokh Ravensbruk.

00:22:07.023 --> 00:22:11.355
Ravensbruk unter vegns

00:22:14.837 --> 00:22:16.991
iz farshidene zakhn

00:22:19.123 --> 00:22:23.719
vos mayn yingere shvester hot dertseylt, vayl zenen tsvey shvesters,

00:22:23.730 --> 00:22:26.866
vayl mit mir iz mitgekumen fun der heym

00:22:26.885 --> 00:22:29.613
a yingere shvester un zey hobn zikh getrofn

00:22:30.024 --> 00:22:32.957
mit protektsye, hobn zey zikh getrofn

00:22:32.977 --> 00:22:35.924
in Oyshvits tsuzamen un dan zenen zey geblibn

00:22:36.167 --> 00:22:39.503
tsuzamen mer veyniker, un azoy oykh evakuirt tsuzamen.

00:22:41.094 --> 00:22:44.733
un zi hot mir vegn dem dertseylt, vayl der,

00:22:45.144 --> 00:22:47.349
der hoypt heldin

00:22:47.591 --> 00:22:49.714
zi hot keyn mol nisht gevolt redn

00:22:49.734 --> 00:22:50.825
vegn dem,

00:22:50.983 --> 00:22:56.313
vayl ales vos zi hot getun iz bay ir gevezn a natirlekhe zakh, dos hot zi gezen in der heym,

00:22:56.349 --> 00:22:59.569
un es kumt ir gornisht derfar. nisht tsu tun iz gevezn

00:22:59.589 --> 00:23:02.283
an aveyre un dos iz nisht geven keyn mitsve

00:23:02.441 --> 00:23:03.397
bay ir.

00:23:07.419 --> 00:23:12.898
iz zi ongekumen nokh Ravensbruk,

00:23:14.169 --> 00:23:16.037
baym araynmarshirn

00:23:16.650 --> 00:23:18.090
hert zi vi me zogt,

00:23:18.090 --> 00:23:22.651
"Tsilka, tomer hostu epes un du vilst es hobn,

00:23:22.843 --> 00:23:24.896
varf es avek, vest es hobn."

00:23:26.741 --> 00:23:29.233
dos iz gevezn meydlekh,

00:23:29.306 --> 00:23:30.634
oder a meydl,

00:23:31.196 --> 00:23:33.401
vos zi iz fun Oyshvits

00:23:34.132 --> 00:23:38.970
als SHTRAFFE

00:23:39.482 --> 00:23:41.133
geshikt gevorn

00:23:41.152 --> 00:23:42.665
nokh Ravensbruk.

00:23:42.823 --> 00:23:44.555
un se geven farshidene.

00:23:45.489 --> 00:23:47.790
nor zi hot zikh dan tsurikgetrofn

00:23:47.801 --> 00:23:51.575
dos vos zi hot avekgevorfn, zi hot avekgevorfn vos hot zi gehat dort:

00:23:52.442 --> 00:23:57.364
farshterkerungs UNK puln, piln, ikh ve- ikh veys nisht genoy UNK.

00:23:57.993 --> 00:23:59.894
aspirinen, filaykht.

00:24:00.828 --> 00:24:02.527
iz tsvishn

00:24:02.583 --> 00:24:08.181
in Ravensbruk hot gekrign groys fiber mayn yingere shvester, Lily.

00:24:08.321 --> 00:24:09.598
oder Laytshu.

00:24:11.308 --> 00:24:13.581
iz mayn shvester iz gegangen

00:24:13.670 --> 00:24:17.309
trots dem vos zi iz gevezn a alte oyshvitser

00:24:18.058 --> 00:24:19.993
heftling,

00:24:20.707 --> 00:24:23.857
hot zi nisht gevust dos gezets fun yedn lager.

00:24:24.015 --> 00:24:26.017
iz zi gegangen in shpitol

00:24:26.141 --> 00:24:33.358
fregn a do- a doktorin vayl zi hot groys fiber, di shvester ire.

00:24:34.325 --> 00:24:36.904
zi kumt tsu tsum toyer zogt men ir,

00:24:36.904 --> 00:24:38.826
"Tsilka, shtey! halt!"

00:24:39.354 --> 00:24:41.086
gibt zi a kuk, ver iz dos.

00:24:41.598 --> 00:24:45.879
oykhet eyner fun di vos me hot zey geshikt fun Oyshvits, oder fun Birkenoy dos,

00:24:46.104 --> 00:24:47.533
SHTRAFFE.

00:24:50.407 --> 00:24:53.878
zogt zi, "gey nisht arayn, vayl do iz do nor eyn tir.

00:24:55.520 --> 00:25:00.898
do geyt men arayn un dan makht me do eksperimentn, ober aroys kumt keyner nisht."

00:25:01.089 --> 00:25:02.073
vos iz?

00:25:02.073 --> 00:25:03.811
hot zi gezogt azoy un azoy,

00:25:03.811 --> 00:25:07.158
zogt, "se do do a doktorin,

00:25:07.873 --> 00:25:09.701
un zi vet kumen tsu dikh."

00:25:09.712 --> 00:25:13.740
un zi iz gekumen, zi hot ir gegebn dort a a ⟨aynshtikh⟩ un dos,

00:25:13.830 --> 00:25:16.147
vayl in a por teg shpeter hobn zey

00:25:16.158 --> 00:25:17.671
vayter gegangen.

00:25:20.225 --> 00:25:22.616
vos a min plats iz Ravensbruk gevezn?

00:25:22.385 --> 00:25:23.476
Estraykh.

00:25:23.702 --> 00:25:29.957
a, Ravensbruk i- iz gevezn a, a a alte farn-krigedikn lager.

00:25:23.752 --> 00:25:27.391
yo, ober voser, ikh meyn a, a lager, oder...

00:25:30.013 --> 00:25:33.146
UNK a SHTRAF-lager fun farn krig, in Estraykh.

00:25:34.434 --> 00:25:36.369
dan ikh

00:25:36.459 --> 00:25:40.312
in estraykher geshikhte, UNK in in in lager geshikhte,

00:25:40.312 --> 00:25:41.654
gefengenishn,

00:25:41.654 --> 00:25:43.423
bin ikh nisht azoy bakant.

00:25:49.622 --> 00:25:52.850
efsher geyen mir a bisl tsurik tsu ayer eygene geshikhte?

00:25:53.643 --> 00:25:56.192
ven ir hot ongehoybn der- tsu dertseyln

00:25:56.203 --> 00:25:59.420
ven di gezetsn akegn di yidn zenen shtarker gevorn.

00:26:00.793 --> 00:26:03.988
umgefer nayntsn dray un fertsik, nayntsn fir un fertsik.

00:26:03.988 --> 00:26:09.866
efsher kent ir a bisl dertseyln vi azoy se hot zikh far ayer mishpokhe, dort in Orsheve, nokh opgeshpilt vayter.

00:26:10.580 --> 00:26:12.532
undz ho'mir shpetsyel nisht

00:26:12.842 --> 00:26:14.608
gelitn vayl,

00:26:15.221 --> 00:26:19.097
vayl dos di di tishleray iz geven ofn.

00:26:20.283 --> 00:26:25.070
un trots dem vos se gevezn a groyse,

00:26:25.818 --> 00:26:28.530
a ratsyon oyf esn,

00:26:29.160 --> 00:26:33.460
iz ober di poyern hobn gebrengt far arbet, hobn zey gebrengt esn.

00:26:33.460 --> 00:26:37.304
azoy oyf dem gebit iz nisht gevezn keyn problem.

00:26:37.985 --> 00:26:42.384
mayn gotzelike foter hot zikh dan shpeter gedarft oykh meldn,

00:26:43.217 --> 00:26:45.878
un me hot gedarft makhn,

00:26:46.608 --> 00:26:48.189
vayl di mentshn

00:26:48.431 --> 00:26:50.653
velkhe zenen

00:26:54.236 --> 00:26:59.563
nisht geven keyn ekhte ungarn, zenen nisht geboyrn dort etlekhe, por generatsyes,

00:26:59.805 --> 00:27:01.841
vayl di mentshn zenen gekumen fun Poyln,

00:27:02.201 --> 00:27:03.832
oder nor fun andere lender,

00:27:04.226 --> 00:27:07.410
hot men zey gefirt nokh Poyln. hot men gemuzt hobn

00:27:07.837 --> 00:27:10.869
a ungarishn birger-rekht.

00:27:13.153 --> 00:27:15.842
nor biz me hot gehat dem birger-rekht,

00:27:17.000 --> 00:27:20.555
hot men zikh gemuzt meldn bay di GENDARMERIE.

00:27:23.160 --> 00:27:24.791
un dos iz gegangen

00:27:26.518 --> 00:27:28.537
biz peysekh fir un fertsik.

00:27:28.813 --> 00:27:34.174
iz es geven a problem tsu bakumen dem birger-rekht, oder ale mentshn vos hobn dort gevoynt hobn gekent bakumen?

00:27:33.099 --> 00:27:34.629
se geven a problem.

00:27:35.310 --> 00:27:37.785
vayl se hot gekost a

00:27:37.892 --> 00:27:39.830
der JOINT hot intervenirt,

00:27:39.849 --> 00:27:41.835
mit gelt un azoy vayter.

00:27:43.764 --> 00:27:46.948
und dos iz gegangen biz fir un fertsik,

00:27:47.223 --> 00:27:48.787
un fir un fertsik

00:27:49.417 --> 00:27:55.925
for Peysekh,

00:27:57.956 --> 00:27:59.638
hot men geheysn

00:28:00.757 --> 00:28:05.139
yeder yid zol kumen in di groyse shul, dort hot men gemakht di geto,

00:28:06.512 --> 00:28:13.239
un me hot geheysn vos veyniker mitbrengen.

00:28:13.211 --> 00:28:15.282
OKAY undz vel'mir do makhn a pauze.

00:28:14.578 --> 00:28:15.366
yo
